data.description: Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this inviting 3 bed/1.1 bath townhome offers comfortable living with modern amenities and convenient access to nearby schools, parks, trails, forests, and a golf course. Spacious living area, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. The large windows flood the room with natural light. The adjoining kitchen boasts ample counter space and plenty of storage, making meal prep a breeze. Upstairs, you'll find 3 comfortable bedrooms; the primary bedroom features generous closet space and easy access to the shared bathroom. Outside, a private patio provides the ideal spot for morning coffee or al fresco dining, surrounded by lush greenery and tranquil surroundings. Located in the highly sought-after Palos with convenient proximity to shopping, dining, and major transportation routes, this townhome offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and community.
